{"tid":1590384,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"關之琳真的老了！0修圖驚人臉蛋曝光 暴露殘酷真相","createTime":"2019-09-23T16:38:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T17:11:11.000Z","uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6c1da80d0a59259a9a0deacfeac9b3dc213660f3","tid":1590384,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:38:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DVV91U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DVV91U.png&h=0de66b05&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h8owJmW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh8owJmW.png&h=3c55acd7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j02NgGX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj02NgGX.png&h=0297079d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h4w2P1Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh4w2P1Y.png&h=ba848af2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「香江第一美人」關之琳出道逾30年，因保養得宜，看不出已57歲，至今仍是不少網友心中的女神，不過她的閨蜜汪詩詩近日提前為她慶生，一張照片卻打回原形，完全暴露出她的真實年齡。<br />\n <br />\n汪詩詩po出替關之琳慶生照片，並寫下「Happy birthday to 姐姐，內外都美麗」，不過細看汪詩詩口中的大美人關之琳，照片中不僅臉蛋臃腫，眼角和下巴更出現驚人皺紋，昔日電眼顯得無神，笑起來也略顯僵硬，讓不少網友表示「美人老啦」、「曾經貌美驚為天人，現在被歲月打磨得美貌盡失！歲月不饒人」，感歎又是一個時代的過去。"},{"pid":"9beb812510380485621b7be0fd805f7ff63f0365","tid":1590384,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:39:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"d7dda151a09a3dc28c9bbdb7264d6b1c6e1090ff","tid":1590384,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T16:39:18.000Z","msg":"我係召集今日喺始創唱國歌嗰個小薯仔，我有啲嘢想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590080\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://